   --c[&Shape]|ghost:&description;The creature must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw against DC [*S:spell_save_dc] or be frightened of the undead until the end of the target’s next turn.|putrid:&description;If the target is poisoned, it must succeed on a Constitution saving throw against DC [*S:spell_save_dc] or be paralyzed until the end of its next turn.|skeletal:&description;
   --=attacks|[$SpellLevel]\2
   --&FesteringDesc|Any creature, other than you, that starts its turn within 5 feet of the spirit must succeed on a Constitution saving throw against DC [*S:spell_save_dc] or be poisoned until the start of its next turn.
   -->SetStats|[$action];[&damage];[&description]
